name: Liof
tagline: Liof is open source to-do list and task manager with shared on the public service - liof.io
body:
### Liof.io
Manage any lists

### List formats
    - Todo
    - Task
    - Checklist
    - Pricelist
    - Wiki
    - Numbered
    - Bulleted

### Built with

    - Ruby on Rails
    - Elasticsearch
    - MongoDB
    - React
